,\\ldots,u_{\\ell}):=\\min_{\\Delta} f_{\\Delta}(n;u_2,\\ldots,u_{\\ell}).$ We\ndetermine $f(n;u_2,\\ldots,u_{\\ell})$ up to a multiplicative logarithm factor.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Feb 2016 23:13:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-12"}
