d to be $4\\times 10^9 - 2 \\times10^{10}$ cm$^{-3}$\n(using the ratio of \\ion{Ca}{XV}~181.90\\AA\\ over \\ion{Ca}{XV}~200.97\\AA). We\ncompare our findings with other works on the same AR to provide a unified\npicture of its evolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Feb 2016 11:23:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-16"}
